# The packaged-app verifier byte-compares ASAR contents against the working
# tree, so checkouts must be line-ending-stable on every platform.
* text=auto eol=lf

# This updater is reviewed by its exact PE bytes. Never subject it to text or
# line-ending normalization, even if a future Git heuristic changes.
/apps/companion/packaging/squirrel-windows/Squirrel.exe binary

# Source patches deliberately preserve upstream context whitespace and encode
# CRLF-only submodule blobs through Git's binary-patch transport.
/.github/patches/squirrel-updater/*.patch -whitespace
